<!doctype html>
<html lang="fr">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <title>PeachComs - Page introuvable</title>
        <link href="/PeachComs/css/stylesheet.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <link href="/PeachComs/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container mt-5 mb-5 text-center" style="max-width: 600px;">
            <p class="text-success mocha mt-5 pt-5" style="font-size: 2rem;">On dirais que tu t'est perdu :(</p>
            <h1 class="mocha text-info display-1 mb-2">404</h1>
            <p class="mocha text-info fs-2 mb-3">Page introuvable !</p>
            <p class="garet fs-5 text-muted mb-4">
                La page que tu cherches n'existe pas ou tu n'as pas accès à celle-ci.
            </p>
            <div class="d-flex gap-3 justify-content-center">
                <a href="/PeachComs/" class="btn btn-info">
                    <span class="garet fw-bold text-light">
                        <i class="bi bi-house-fill"></i> Retour à l'accueil
                    </span>
                </a>
                <a href="/PeachComs/commissions" class="btn btn-outline-dark">
                    <span class="garet fw-bold">
                        <i class="bi bi-palette-fill"></i> Voir les commissions
                    </span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>